---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Retail EV Charging Solutions — Evium Charging"
  description="Turn your parking lot into a destination. Evium delivers turnkey EV charging for retail properties — no capital investment, managed end-to-end, drives foot traffic and dwell time."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center bg-evium-dark overflow-hidden pt-20">
    <!-- Background gradient orbs -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-evium-green/5 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-evium-green/4 rounded-full blur-[140px]"></div>
    </div>
    <!-- Grid texture -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]"
         style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;">
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <!-- Eyebrow -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
          <span class="text-evium-green text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">Retail Solutions</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-none tracking-tight text-white mb-8">
          Your Parking Lot Is&nbsp;a<br />
          <span class="text-evium-green">Competitive Advantage.</span><br />
          Use&nbsp;It.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-12">
          EV drivers choose where to shop based on where they can charge. Evium installs, manages, and maintains your charging infrastructure — at no cost to you — so your property becomes the destination they keep coming back to.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact/quote"
             class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-evium-green text-evium-dark font-bold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-white transition-colors duration-200">
            Get a Free Site Assessment
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#opportunity"
             class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-white/20 text-white font-semibold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:border-evium-green hover:text-evium-green transition-colors duration-200">
            See How It Works
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat bar -->
        <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 border-t border-white/10 pt-12 max-w-2xl">
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-evium-green">500+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/50 mt-1">Chargers Deployed</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-evium-green">$0</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/50 mt-1">Owner Investment Required</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-evium-green">100%</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/50 mt-1">Managed by Evium</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       THE RETAIL CHARGING OPPORTUNITY
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="opportunity" class="bg-evium-dark-light py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <span class="w-6 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
            <span class="text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">The Opportunity</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-8">
            EV Drivers Pick<br />
            <span class="text-evium-green">Where to Shop</span><br />
            Based on Where<br />
            They Can Charge.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The U.S. has tens of millions of EVs on the road — and that number is growing every year. These drivers are actively searching for charging destinations. The retail property with chargers wins the visit.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            It's not just about attracting new customers. Charging extends dwell time. A shopper who plugs in while they browse stays longer, spends more, and comes back because your location fits their routine.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-evium-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-2">Destination Routing</h3>
            <p class="text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed">EV navigation apps and charging networks surface your property to nearby drivers actively looking for a place to charge. Visibility you can't buy any other way.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-evium-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-2">Extended Dwell Time</h3>
            <p class="text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed">A plugged-in customer is a captive audience. They're not leaving until the charge is done — and while they wait, they browse, eat, and spend. Charging is a revenue multiplier.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-evium-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-2">First-Mover Advantage</h3>
            <p class="text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed">Most retail lots in your market don't have EV charging yet. The property that installs first captures the habit — and habitual customers are the most valuable customers you have.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       L2 VS DCFC FOR RETAIL
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-evium-dark py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="w-6 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
          <span class="text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">Choosing the Right Hardware</span>
          <span class="w-6 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight">
          Level 2 or DC Fast?<br />
          <span class="text-evium-green">The Answer Depends on Your Format.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-white/55 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Evium assesses your property type, traffic patterns, and customer dwell time to recommend the right mix — then designs the layout for maximum utilization.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- L2 Card -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-10 border border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-48 h-48 bg-evium-green/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-evium-green/10 text-evium-green text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6">
              Level 2 — Up to 19.2 kW
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4">Best for Longer Dwell Formats</h3>
            <p class="text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Grocery anchors, big-box stores, lifestyle centers, and strip malls with 1–3 hour average visits are ideal for Level 2. Customers arrive, plug in, shop their list, and leave with meaningful charge added — typically 20–40 miles per hour of session.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-white/70 text-sm">Grocery, big-box, lifestyle, strip centers</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-white/70 text-sm">1–3 hour average customer visits</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-white/70 text-sm">Lower infrastructure cost, more stalls per dollar</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-white/70 text-sm">Wall-mount or pedestal configurations</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- DCFC Card -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-10 border border-evium-green/20 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-48 h-48 bg-evium-green/8 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-evium-green/15 text-evium-green text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6">
              DC Fast — 60–240 kW
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4">Best for High-Turnover Locations</h3>
            <p class="text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Quick-service retail, convenience-anchored centers, or high-visibility pad sites benefit from DC fast charging. A 30-minute session delivers 60–100+ miles — matching the typical quick-stop visit and commanding premium session pricing.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-white/70 text-sm">Quick-service, convenience, pad site retail</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-white/70 text-sm">15–45 minute session durations</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-white/70 text-sm">High revenue per session, higher stall turns</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-white/70 text-sm">Outdoor kiosk format, dual-port CCS/CHAdeMO</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5 text-center">
        <p class="text-white/70 text-base">
          <span class="text-evium-green font-semibold">Most retail properties benefit from a mix.</span> Evium designs the right combination based on your lot layout, electrical capacity, and customer profile — then handles every aspect of delivery.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       WHAT EVIUM DELIVERS
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-evium-dark-light py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="w-6 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
          <span class="text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">Turnkey Delivery</span>
          <span class="w-6 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white">
          Everything Done for You.<br />
          <span class="text-evium-green">Nothing Left to Manage.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0021 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-.553-.894L15 4m0 13V4m0 0L9 7"/>`,
            title: "Site Assessment & Design",
            desc: "Evium engineers evaluate your electrical infrastructure, lot layout, and customer traffic patterns to design a deployment built for maximum impact."
          },
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>`,
            title: "Hardware Selection",
            desc: "We source and configure commercial-grade Level 2 and DC fast chargers matched to your format — wall-mount, pedestal, or outdoor kiosk as needed."
          },
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/>`,
            title: "Permits & Compliance",
            desc: "Evium manages all permitting, utility coordination, and code compliance so you don't have to navigate a single municipal process or inspection."
          },
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 8v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>`,
            title: "Payment Processing Integration",
            desc: "QR code tap-to-pay, RFID card, and the Evium driver app — all integrated at installation. Customers pay instantly, and revenue flows to your account automatically."
          },
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>`,
            title: "Real-Time Monitoring & Reporting",
            desc: "The Evium owner portal gives you live visibility into session data, revenue, uptime, and usage trends — accessible from any device, any time."
          },
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"/>`,
            title: "Ongoing Maintenance",
            desc: "Hardware faults, connectivity issues, and routine servicing are Evium's responsibility. If a charger goes down, we fix it — not your facilities team."
          }
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-evium-green/30 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" set:html={item.icon}></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       REVENUE & MONETIZATION
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-evium-dark py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <span class="w-6 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
            <span class="text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">Revenue & Monetization</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-8">
            Your Parking Lot<br />
            <span class="text-evium-green">Generates Revenue.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Every charging session puts money in your pocket. Evium's software lets you set custom pricing — per kWh, per hour, or a flat session fee — so you control the economics for your market and customer mix.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-10">
            Under Evium's no-cost model, we cover the full capital investment and you receive passive income from day one. No upfront spend, no ongoing overhead — just revenue deposited automatically into your account.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span class="text-white/70">Custom pricing: per kWh, per hour, or flat session fee</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span class="text-white/70">Revenue reporting dashboard with session-level detail</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span class="text-white/70">Automatic revenue distribution — no manual reconciliation</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span class="text-white/70">Idle fee configuration to encourage stall turnover</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pricing model visual -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-7 border border-evium-green/20">
